  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0b9a\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0bb5\u0b95\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1\u0bb4\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0b9f\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b87\u0ba9\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0b9a\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bc8 \u0ba4\u0bc0\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0bb5\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbe\u0ba9 \u0b8e\u0bb4\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bc2\u0bb2 \u0b89\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bb0\u0bb5\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bcb\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0bc1\u0bae\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0ba9\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Sumanthran requested the all-party committee for a written guarantee to solve the ethnic problem",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Tamil National Federation has set conditions and demanded guarantees for participation in an all-party interim government.",
        "The federation has insisted that if an all-party interim government is to be formed, the plan of operations of the government should be disclosed in advance and a written guarantee of the solution of the national ethnic problem should be given.",
        "A political restructuring committee headed by Dr. Rajitha Senaratne has been established for this discussion.",
        "The meeting of the committee was held last Friday at the office of the Leader of the Opposition in Colombo.",
        "Rajitasenaratne, Eron Wickramaratne, Ranjith Mathumabandara, Anurapriyadarsana Yappa, Dayasiri Jayasekara, Dumintha Dissanayake, Lasantha Ajjaya Vanna, Sumandran, Manokanesan, Jeevan Thondaman, Vasudeva Nanayakkara and others participated in the meeting.",
        "During this, there was an in-depth discussion regarding the formation of the All-Party Interim Government and the issues to be focused on. Sumanthran commented to Veerakesari regarding this discussion.",
        "We are continuously holding discussions regarding the formation of an all-party interim government.",
        "Regarding the participation of the Tamil National Federation in this, the final decision will be taken after discussion in the Sri Lankan Tamil Republic Party and the Federation.",
        "However, participating in the discussion as a representative of the Federation, I clarified our continued position to other party representatives.",
        "In particular, if an all-party interim government is to be formed, I requested that a map regarding the next steps of that government should be disclosed.",
        "I also mentioned that based on that, the All Party of the Federation will decide whether to participate in the interim government or not.",
        "Also, most importantly, the All-Party Interim Government that will be established should without delay create a new constitution in which powers are distributed in order to achieve a solution to the national ethnic problem in this country.",
        "Abolition of executive power presidential system, establishment of independent committees, giving powers to the parliament should also be included in the constitution so formed.",
        "I have requested all parties participating in the All-Party Government to give a written undertaking covering these matters.",
        "He said that other parties have accepted the rationale in the matter and extensive discussions about these areas will continue."
      ],
